PHASE-SPECIFIC PROMPTS:

```json
{
  "phases": {
    "discovery": {
      "goal": "Understand user needs and qualify",
      "prompt_template": "Continue discovery conversation. Ask about their current challenges and goals. User profile: {{user_profile}}. Topics not yet covered: {{uncovered_topics}}",
      "max_turns": 5,
      "transition_triggers": ["high_interest", "budget_confirmed"]
